          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Arbitration Transparency Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill specifies that an arbitration proceeding between a consumer and a financial institution, in a dispute involving a consumer financial product or service, must be open to the public.</p>]]></text>
